docs.text: v3 API reference This contains the v3 API reference. GET /v3/cats Returns a list of all cats. GET /v3/breeds Returns a list of all breeds of cats. GET /v3/breeds/:breed_name/cats Returns a list of all cats under the :breed_name breed. GET /v3/search Parameters: q = A string containing the search query for a cat name or breed. Returns a list of cats that match the search query. Markdown source: sample-docs/v3/docs/reference.md Permalink: https://spotify.github.io/mkdocs-monorepo-plugin/monorepo-example/versions/v3/reference/ GET /v3/cat/:name/lives_left Returns how many lives the cat named :name still has left.
